# Write a Python program to find sum of digits of a three digit number

num = int(input("Enter a three-digit number: "))
digit1 = num // 100
digit2 = (num // 10) % 10
digit3 = num % 10
sum = digit1 + digit2 + digit3
print("Sum of digits is", sum)

# OUTPUT
'''
Enter a three-digit number: 123
Sum of digits is 6
'''
